title: CATCH 22 - Joseph Heller. Read by Wolfram Kandinsky {FerraBit}
description:
CATCH-22 by Joseph Heller (1961)

Read by . . : Wolfram Kandinsky.
Publisher . : Books On Tape, Inc. 1980
ISBN . . . .: ISBN-10: 0736689621
Format . . .: MP3.  ~64 kbps (iTunes 8, VBR, mono), 194 tracks, 375 MB.
Source . . .: Cassette > CD > MP3 
Unabridged

This recording (on cassette tape only) is currently out of print.
Sadly, Books On Tape report they can not sell or replace the cassettes.

I transferred from cassette, to CD, to MP3 (96kbps VBR).

My opinion: the Kandinsky reading captures the essense of the book, 
while other readers detract, or distract, from the essence/spirit 
of the book. I just can't listen to the other recordings of it.
